api endpoints


1. auth
//public routes
post /api/auth/register
post /api/auth/login

//protected routes
get /api/auth/me


2.project - all routes protected

// Project CRUD
get /api/projects/
post /api/projects/
get /api/projects/:id
patch /api/projects/:id
deelte /api/projects/:id

// Member management
post /api/projects/:id/members
delete /api/projects/:id/members/:userId

3. Task  - all routes protected
 
// Project-based task routes
get /api/tasks/projects/:projectId/tasks
post /api/tasks/projects/:projectId/tasks

// Task-specific routes
get /api/tasks/:id
patch  /api/tasks/:id
patch  /api/tasks/:id/reorder
delete  /api/tasks/:id


4.comment - all routes protected 

// Task-based comment routes
get /api/comments/tasks/:taskId/comments
post   /api/comments/tasks/:taskId/comments

// Comment-specific routes
delete /api/comments/:id


5. dashboard - all routes protected

get  /api/dashboard/overview

